00:09:07.630 --> 00:09:11.380
It is that fundamental belief--
I am my brother's keeper,

00:09:11.380 --> 00:09:16.280
I am my sister's keeper--
that makes this country work.

00:09:16.280 --> 00:09:20.560
It's what allows us to
pursue our individual dreams,

00:09:20.560 --> 00:09:24.740
and yet still come together
as one American family.

00:09:24.740 --> 00:09:26.750
E pluribus unum.

00:09:26.750 --> 00:09:30.310
Out of many, one.

00:09:30.310 --> 00:09:32.800
Now, even as we
speak, there are those

00:09:32.800 --> 00:09:34.990
who are preparing to divide us.

00:09:34.990 --> 00:09:38.000
The spin masters, the
negative-ad peddlers,

00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:41.920
who embrace the politics
of anything goes.

00:09:41.920 --> 00:09:44.850
Well, I say to
them tonight, there

00:09:44.850 --> 00:09:48.210
is not a liberal America
and a conservative America.

00:09:48.210 --> 00:09:50.505
There is the United
States of America.

00:09:50.505 --> 00:09:52.165
[CHEERING]

00:09:52.165 --> 00:09:55.695
There is not a black
America and a white America,

00:09:55.695 --> 00:09:58.880
a Latino America,
an Asian America.

00:09:58.880 --> 00:10:01.115
There's the United
States of America.

00:10:01.115 --> 00:10:04.280
[CHEERING]

00:10:04.280 --> 00:10:08.430
The pundits-- the pundits like
to slice and dice our country

00:10:08.430 --> 00:10:10.980
into red states and blue states.

00:10:10.980 --> 00:10:14.370
Red states for Republicans,
blue states for Democrats.

00:10:14.370 --> 00:10:15.740
But I've got news for them, too.

00:10:15.740 --> 00:10:18.700
We worship an awesome
god in the blue states,

00:10:18.700 --> 00:10:21.730
and we don't like Federal agents
poking around in our libraries

00:10:21.730 --> 00:10:22.580
in the red states.

00:10:22.580 --> 00:10:25.460
[CHEERING]

00:10:25.460 --> 00:10:28.160
We coach little league
in the blue states,

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:30.430
and yes, we've got some Gay
friends in the red states.

00:10:30.430 --> 00:10:32.204
[CHEERING]

00:10:32.204 --> 00:10:35.340
There are patriots who
opposed the war in Iraq,

00:10:35.340 --> 00:10:37.555
and there are patriots who
supported the war in Iraq.

00:10:37.555 --> 00:10:38.138
