And then I remember hearing him.

00:11:12.169 --> 00:11:13.210
I didn't know who he was.

00:11:13.210 --> 00:11:14.560
I'd never heard of him before.

00:11:14.560 --> 00:11:18.970
And I remember hearing his
voice, and doing a double-take.

00:11:18.970 --> 00:11:22.570
Sitting down on the end of my
bed and listening to his talk,

00:11:22.570 --> 00:11:24.840
and thinking, he's
going to be somebody.

00:11:24.840 --> 00:11:26.490
Little did I know.

00:11:26.490 --> 00:11:28.340
Four years later,
he's president.

00:11:28.340 --> 00:11:30.400
Four years later,
he's president.

