going to learn so much about how

00:18:09.920 --> 00:18:13.340
to be a great speaker.

00:18:13.340 --> 00:18:15.300
So what I'm doing
is, I'm contradicting

00:18:15.300 --> 00:18:18.430
what I'm saying with my body
language and my movements.

00:18:18.430 --> 00:18:22.160
Now, you know, people complain
to me when I give that example.

00:18:22.160 --> 00:18:25.290
And, well, Ruth, you're
a professional speaker.

00:18:25.290 --> 00:18:26.620
