00:41:27.060 --> 00:41:28.260
He has a book.

00:41:28.260 --> 00:41:29.530
You should get this book.

00:41:29.530 --> 00:41:31.380
It's called "Words That Work."

00:41:31.380 --> 00:41:35.370
It's not what you say,
it's what people hear.

00:41:35.370 --> 00:41:37.150
Not what you say,
it's what people hear.

