00:42:38.410 --> 00:42:39.260
Right?

00:42:39.260 --> 00:42:39.774
Estates?

00:42:39.774 --> 00:42:40.690
That's from Greenwich.

00:42:40.690 --> 00:42:42.480
That's where I live, in
Greenwich, Connecticut.

00:42:42.480 --> 00:42:44.688
You know, that's where the
estates-- and around here.

00:42:44.688 --> 00:42:48.060
That's really the estates are.

00:42:48.060 --> 00:42:53.030
As I mentioned,
Democrat as a one-word

00:42:53.030 --> 00:42:55.700
frame that you
