piece of that?

00:44:48.220 --> 00:44:50.460
Because that's what
a good frame does.

00:44:50.460 --> 00:44:52.400
It makes you feel good.

00:44:52.400 --> 00:44:53.860
It makes you feel better.

00:44:53.860 --> 00:44:56.234
It makes you think that your
life is going to be better,

00:44:56.234 --> 00:44:57.650
or your work, or
your business, is

00:44:57.650 --> 00:45:01.160
going to be easier, if you do
what it is that you're saying,

00:45:01.160 --> 00:45:02.760
if you framed it the right way.

00:45:02.760 --> 00:45:04.300
So start thinking about that.

